column2: Do you consider yourself to be an older adult?
column3: I have heard _______________ about age discrimination.
column4: In recent years I have been discriminated against or treated more negatively by others because of my older age.
column5: In recent years I have avoided certain social settings out of concern that I might be treated negatively because of my age.
column6: Age discrimination is too often excused.
column7: Age discrimination is a major problem in our society.
column8: I have had experiences with age discrimination that have caused me mental or emotional stress.
column9: Age discrimination is taken too seriously.
column10: Have you or anyone you know ever seen or been the target of discrimination in the workplace based on older age?
column11: Have you or anyone you know ever seen or been the target of discrimination based on older age while applying or interviewing for jobs?
column12: Have you or anyone you know ever seen discriminatory depictions of older age in product marketing or advertisements?
column13: Have you or anyone you know ever seen discriminatory depictions of older age in television shows or movies?
column14: How acceptable do you believe it is for organizations to use age-related information in algorithms to show you targeted ads for products and services?
column15: How acceptable do you believe it is for organizations to use age-related information in algorithms to review employment applications?
column16: How acceptable do you believe it is for organizations to use age-related information in algorithms to review applications for social services?
column17: Have you ever been aware of an automated algorithm used to review an application of yours for a job or employment?
column18: Have you ever been aware of an automated algorithm used to present you with a product advertisement?
column19: Have you ever been aware of an automated algorithm used to review an application of yours for a public or social service?
